  <fr:mainmatter>
  <fr:p>Univalence follows from the closure of families of <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="//erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> types under dependent products (<fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001A.xml" title="Dependent product of contractible types" addr="//erct/erct-001A" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="//erct/erct-001A" /></fr:link>) via the distributivity of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\prod ]]></fr:tex> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\sum ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter>
