            <fr:title text="Dependent product of contractible types">Dependent product of <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="//erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> types</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Lemma</fr:taxon>
            <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-001A.agda" type="external">erct-001A.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Given a dependent function <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f : \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx}]]></fr:tex>, if each component <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Bx]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="//erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> with centre <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[fx]]></fr:tex> then the dependent product <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx}]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="//erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link> with centre <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
